        - Fix warnings with Perl 5.21 (GH-1).

v1.0.3  2014-06-08
        - Bumped git requirement to v1.7.4.1.
        - Made git test safer to run.

v1.0.2  2014-06-02
        - Sync manifest.

v1.0.1  2014-06-01
        - Fix replacing environment variables in the update file path.

v1.0.0  2014-05-31
        - Public release.
